messages.content:
THOUGHT: The crash happens because an insertelement used to build a pointer vector does not dominate a subsequent shufflevector that uses it. A minimal and robust fix is to relocate the freshly created insertelement to a block that dominates its uses when needed. Specifically, right after creating the InsertElementInst, if its parent block does not dominate the current IRBuilder insertion block, and the inserted scalar is not an instruction (e.g., function argument/constant), move the insertelement to the beginning of the current insertion block (skipping allocas in the entry block). This preserves correctness and minimizes ordering changes elsewhere.

```bash
python3 - << 'PY' && /llvm-autofix/build/llvm-build/128770/bin/opt -S --passes=slp-vectorizer -mtriple=x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu -mcpu=skylake /tmp/test.ll >/dev/null && submit-patch
from pathlib import Path
import re
p = Path("llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp")
s = p.read_text()

# Insert dominance-fix move right after insertelement creation.
pattern = re.compile(
    r'(InsElt\s*=\s*dyn_cast<InsertElementInst>\(Vec\);\s*\n\s*if\s*\(!InsElt\)\s*return\s*Vec;\s*)',
    re.S
)
insertion = r"""\1
      // Ensure the insertelement dominates all subsequent uses created by this builder.
      // If the scalar is not an instruction (e.g., argument/constant) and the newly
      // created insertelement does not dominate the current insertion block, move it.
      if (!isa<Instruction>(Scalar)) {
        if (BasicBlock *UseBB = Builder.GetInsertBlock()) {
          BasicBlock *DefBB = InsElt->getParent();
          if (DefBB != UseBB && (!DT || !DT->dominates(DefBB, UseBB))) {
            // Move to the first valid insertion point of the use block.
            auto FI = UseBB->getFirstInsertionPt();
            if (UseBB == &UseBB->getParent()->getEntryBlock()) {
              // Skip allocas in the entry block.
              auto It = UseBB->begin();
              while (It != UseBB->end() && isa<AllocaInst>(&*It))
                ++It;
              if (It != UseBB->end())
                InsElt->moveBefore(&*It);
              else if (FI != UseBB->end())
                InsElt->moveBefore(&*FI);
            } else if (FI != UseBB->end()) {
              InsElt->moveBefore(&*FI);
            }
          }
        }
      }
"""
ns, n = pattern.subn(insertion, s, count=1)
if n == 0:
    raise SystemExit("Failed to locate insertelement site for dominance fix.")
p.write_text(ns)
PY
```

